commitResults.messageTitle: Implement date and time in tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
Allows bot to read & display date and time for deadlines and events
Bot reads dates in format: "yyyy-mm-dd" and time in 24hr format
Bot displays dates in format: "MONTH dd yyyy" and time in 12hr format
Abstraction for printing and reading operations
